    SFM --> BGD[Blue-Green Deployment<br/>Progressive: 0%→10%→25%→50%→100%]
    SFM --> AP[Adapter Pattern<br/>Zero-downtime compatibility]
    SFM --> FF[Feature Flags<br/>Instant rollback capability]
    BGD --> RB1[Rollback Time: 30 seconds]
    
